   "source": [
    "# 图像噪声与滤波实验\n",
    "\n",
    "本实验基于 **OpenCV + skimage**，完成以下内容：\n",
    "\n",
    "1. 图像读取与颜色空间转换（BGR / RGB / Gray）  \n",
    "2. 添加椒盐噪声与高斯噪声  \n",
    "3. 均值滤波、中值滤波、高斯滤波效果对比  \n",
    "4. 手动实现彩色图像中值滤波算法"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# ===================== 导入依赖库 =====================\n",
    "import cv2\n",
    "from skimage.util import random_noise\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "from matplotlib import pyplot as plt"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. 读取原始图像"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "img = cv2.imread('p1.jpg')\n",
    "\n",
    "# 获取像素点 (100, 100) 的 BGR 值\n",
    "(b, g, r) = img[100, 100]\n",
    "print('Pixel (100,100) BGR:', b, g, r)\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.imshow(img)\n",
    "plt.title('Original Image (BGR)')\n",
    "plt.savefig('result/original_bgr.jpg', dpi=300)\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. 颜色空间转换"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# BGR → RGB\n",
    "rgb_img = cv2.cvtColor(img, cv2.COLOR_BGR2RGB)\n",
    "plt.imshow(rgb_img)\n",
    "plt.title('RGB Image')\n",
    "plt.savefig('result/rgb_image.jpg', dpi=300)\n",
    "plt.show()\n",
    "\n",
    "# BGR → Gray\n",
    "gray_img = cv2.cvtColor(img, cv2.COLOR_BGR2GRAY)\n",
    "plt.imshow(gray_img, cmap='gray')\n",
    "plt.title('Gray Image')\n",
    "plt.savefig('result/gray_image.jpg', dpi=300)\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 3. 添加噪声（椒盐噪声 & 高斯噪声）"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 椒盐噪声\n",
    "sp_noise_img = random_noise(rgb_img, mode='s&p', amount=0.4)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 高斯噪声\n",
    "gus_noise_img = random_noise(rgb_img, mode='gaussian', mean=0.2, var=0.03)\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.figure(figsize=(10, 4))\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.subplot(1, 3, 1)\n",
    "plt.imshow(rgb_img)\n",
    "plt.title('Original Image')\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.subplot(1, 3, 2)\n",
    "plt.imshow(sp_noise_img)\n",
    "plt.title('S&P Noise')\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.subplot(1, 3, 3)\n",
    "plt.imshow(gus_noise_img)\n",
    "plt.title('Gaussian Noise')\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "plt.savefig('result/noise_comparison.jpg', dpi=300)\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 4. 图像滤波（均值 / 中值 / 高斯）"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 均值滤波\n",
    "mean_sp = cv2.blur(sp_noise_img, (5, 5))\n",
    "mean_gus = cv2.blur(gus_noise_img, (5, 5))\n",
    "\n",
    "# 中值滤波（需 uint8）\n",
    "mid_sp = cv2.medianBlur((sp_noise_img * 255).astype(np.uint8), 5)\n",
    "mid_gus = cv2.medianBlur((gus_noise_img * 255).astype(np.uint8), 5)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 高斯滤波\n",
    "gauss_sp = cv2.GaussianBlur((sp_noise_img * 255).astype(np.uint8), (5, 5), 0)\n",
    "gauss_gus = cv2.GaussianBlur((gus_noise_img * 255).astype(np.uint8), (5, 5), 0)"
   ]
  },
